{"tid":2445864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長者打科興 「登記時冇復必泰 依家冇辦法」","createTime":"2021-03-14T03:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T06:18:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5694f93c4781dd5e7115920671ce3995542a8a21","tid":2445864,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"衞生署周六（13日）晚上公佈一宗接種疫苗的嚴重異常事故，事主為63歲男子，於本月9日接種科興疫苗後，翌日開始感身體虛弱，13日情況轉差，往北區醫院急症室求醫，轉送深切治療部，初步診斷為急性中風，現時情況危殆。另早前兩宗年齡分別80歲及67歲男子，接種科興疫苗後感不適，送入深切治療部，兩人分別於13日下午離世。截至13日晚上11時，本港兩周內共6宗接種科興疫苗後死亡個案。惟仍有部份市民對接種疫苗充滿信心，今早續有市民到官涌體育館接種疫苗，有長者表示登記時只有科興，未有復必泰疫苗，「依家冇辦法，惟有選擇科興！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210314/EBS5HSSBONAJDFIGPSUJK6HQ3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210314%2FEBS5HSSBONAJDFIGPSUJK6HQ3I%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=805bc76f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210314%2FEBS5HSSBONAJDFIGPSUJK6HQ3I%2F&h=32c0d938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210314/EBS5HSSBONAJDFIGPSUJK6HQ3I/</a>"},{"pid":"474cd4bb063d5f8e80c6ede7c664c86b0a21ce67","tid":2445864,"uid":170335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:51:47.000Z","msg":"細時唔射波<br />\n大個打科興"},{"pid":"e631a7391dee147b2f908b960319611bef0b368e","tid":2445864,"uid":103230,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSIWzuLeewvyKXU-aQ3wV-0f2eqI810LgweyA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSIWzuLeewvyKXU-aQ3wV-0f2eqI810LgweyA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=ffdcde41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d423835cdd7173508921bdfddfde44ad485b01d9","tid":2445864,"uid":2959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"